## Constraints

- State machine strict — invalid transition → 409 `PROCESS_INVALID_TRANSITION`
- KTİ'de workflow determination workflow class'ta, service'te değil
- Document scan status: PENDING → SCANNING → CLEAN (or INFECTED)
- Process start → document scan CLEAN zorunlu (PENDING/SCANNING → 425)
- Manager assignee → initiator.manager_user_id (yoksa 422 throw)
- display_id generation: PostgreSQL sequence (`process_kti_sequence`)
- Transaction: process + first task + documents link + assignees — atomic

## Done Definition

- [ ] ProcessTypeRegistry pattern çalışıyor — yeni workflow eklemek tek register call
- [ ] KTİ workflow state machine test exhaustive (valid + invalid transitions)
- [ ] KTİ embedded start endpoint: `POST /processes/kti/start`
- [ ] Document upload flow: `POST /documents/upload-initiate` → presigned S3 URL → client upload → `POST /documents/mark-scanning` → scan → `GET /documents/:id` status poll
- [ ] ClamAV integration (worker scan job)
- [ ] Process detail shows timeline, assignees, documents, reason fields
- [ ] KTİ start form multi-step (validate → review → submit)
- [ ] Cancel endpoint — non-terminal → CANCELLED, active task SKIPPED_BY_ROLLBACK
- [ ] Rollback endpoint — previous step'e yeni task
- [ ] Integration test: KTİ full happy path + revision path + reject
- [ ] E2E test: KTİ start (critical journey 2)

## Explicit Don'ts

- Other process types (5S, TPM) — post-MVP
- Video upload (only PDF + image)
- Document versioning — immutable once uploaded
- Process parallel tasks — strictly sequential for KTİ
- Custom state machine editor — spec-based only

